## Campaign Planning Workflow

Follow this process:

- [ ] 1. Brief Analysis: Understand campaign objectives ({{objective}}), target audience ({{target_audience}}), and budget ({{budget}})
- [ ] 2. Audience Segmentation: Define audience segments and their media consumption habits
- [ ] 3. Channel Strategy: Select optimal channels based on audience and objectives
- [ ] 4. Budget Allocation: Distribute budget across channels with rationale
- [ ] 5. Timeline: Create campaign schedule with key milestones
- [ ] 6. KPI Framework: Define success metrics and tracking approach

## Key Inputs
- Client: {{client_name}}
- Objective: {{objective}}
- Target Audience: {{target_audience}}
- Budget: {{budget}}
- Timeline: {{timeline}}
- Competitors: {{competitors}}
